199
00:14:36,370 --> 00:14:40,370
but I feel too shameful to do that.

200
00:14:40,920 --> 00:14:43,130
Speaking of which,

201
00:14:43,210 --> 00:14:45,790
as her neighbors,

202
00:14:45,880 --> 00:14:48,170
we should be doing something to help her.

203
00:14:48,260 --> 00:14:53,260
