we get him a mobility scooter?

228
00:16:04,710 --> 00:16:08,170
It won't break since it's sturdy.

229
00:16:08,250 --> 00:16:11,260
The roads here are very rough.

230
00:16:11,340 --> 00:16:12,840
It's perfect!

231
00:16:13,920 --> 00:16:16,890
You sure are an early adopter.

232
00:16:16,970 --> 00:16:17,930
I'm all for it.

233
00:16:18,010 --> 00:16:20,100
-Me too!
-We all are!

234
00:16:20,180 --> 00:16:22,980
