257
00:17:35,010 --> 00:17:36,130
Right?

258
00:17:36,220 --> 00:17:39,090
Yes, sir. I'm very happy.

259
00:17:39,180 --> 00:17:42,010
It's the first time
I've planted something and seen it grow.

260
00:17:43,100 --> 00:17:45,220
